				<h1>Advocacy at BAYADA</h1>

				<h2 class="bold">Why we advocate for home health care</h2>

				<p>BAYADA Home Health Care has a Government Affairs Office whose purpose is to ensure that policy decisions in Washington, D.C., and in our state and local governments help &#8212; rather than hurt &#8212; BAYADA <a class="go" rel="leanModal" href="#client">clients</a> and our employees. We can’t do this alone—and that is why we have the Hearts for Home Care program. Hearts for Home Care provides a platform where each of us can make our voices heard. When you become a Heart for Home Care, you make a real difference on the issues that positively impact the care we provide our clients.</p>

				

